{"tid":1851804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽， 唔係\"唔割\"唔係\"支持\"， 而係感激醫護為全港人性命而以罷工迫使政府封關","createTime":"2020-01-30T07:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T01:16:39.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e505def8755d850a043e4f644d3d14783039d40","tid":1851804,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"正視聽， 醫護為全港人性命而以罷工迫使政府封關， 所以我地係應該感激感謝醫護， 多謝佢地付出，而唔係就咁講句&quot;唔割&quot;同講句&quot;支持&quot;就算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時手足做野都一樣， 多謝都無句，就咁講唔割就算， 手足冒咁大風險做咁多野， 我地係要講感激感謝手足"},{"pid":"2f67fe6288a77207ab9510156649b70ff780556c","tid":1851804,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"【山下智久2019日劇《破案神手》神預言疫症封城】BSL 4 生化武器大爆發人傳人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9p2zNMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9p2zNMD.jpg&h=0c2cce10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b10Noj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb10Noj2.jpg&h=5cbccfdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n破案神手 第10集（驚異の致死率100％新型エボラ襲来&hellip;<br />\n村を全面封鎖!!）<br />\n<a href=\"https://v.gimy.tv/play/50940-1-10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fv.gimy.tv%2Fplay%2F50940-1-10.html&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=22fa871c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://v.gimy.tv/play/50940-1-10.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rkEYTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rkEYTe.jpg&h=4d66fdef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24c9ec9143e30302e69ca348fd96acf4706f1b35","tid":1851804,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"勞工法例<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/text_alternative/pdf/tc/09.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftext_alternative%2Fpdf%2Ftc%2F09.pdf&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=cd63eda1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/text_alternative/pdf/tc/09.pdf</a><br />\n僱員在以下情況，亦可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">即時終止僱傭合約</span></span></strong>，而無須預先通知或給予代通<br />\n知金：<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合理地恐懼身體會受到暴力或疾病的危害；</span></strong></span><br />\n2. 受僱主苛待；或<br />\n3. 已為僱主連續工作不少於 5 年，而經註冊醫生或註冊中醫發出指定<br />\n的證明書，證明永久不適合擔任現時的工作（請參閱第十一章）。"},{"pid":"5747918aef894f26a584f14c9ecdee07265fec85","tid":1851804,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}